#Questions

https://www.hackerrank.com/contests/microverse-coding-challenges/challenges/chocolate-feast/problem


#Solutions

#Ruby

def chocolateFeast(n, c, m)
    g = n / c
    choco = g
    while(g >= m)
        rem = g / m
        re = g % m
        g = rem + re
        choco += rem
    end
    choco
end
